results.name: Expansion of Product_{i=1..m} (1 + x^(4*i-1)) for m = 12.
comment: Product_{i=1..m} (1 + x^(4*i-1)) is the Poincaré polynomial for both Sp(2m) and O(2m+1).
reference: H. Weyl, The Classical Groups, Princeton, 1946, see p. 238.
